Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBViewWasteLog

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBViewWasteLog
public class JDBViewWasteLog
extends java.lang.Object
The JDBViewWasteLog class updates the table VIEW_WASTE_LOG. This table contains a single row for each unique Waste Location as stored in the VIEW_WASTE_LOG table.

See Also:
JDBWasteReasons, JDBWasteReportingIDS, JDBWasteTransactionType, JDBWasteLocationReporting, JDBWasteTypes, JDBWasteMaterial, JDBWasteLog
